  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 orphan claim)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A central credibility claim is registered and referenced via bindsClaim; supporting evidence documents were reviewed during the assessment but the structured provenance link from the claim to that evidence was inadvertently omitted, leaving the claim unsupported in the formal record.",
