    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been reviewed. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing epistemic gaps. The central credibility claim that hemolysis remains below the clinical threshold is registered in the package record and is considered supported by the evidence reviewed during the assessment. The decision is recorded as Accepted for package completeness purposes pending resolution of the identified gaps.",
